Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:03.64,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here y'go, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:13.59,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's my recommended souvenirs list! \NDun da-da-dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:14.70,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Raw yatsuhashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.81,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ganso, Honke, or Honten would be accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.15,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The classic: oil blotting paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:29.62,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to get enough for Mom, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:31.34,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,And the much-anticipated number one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.09,list_00:31,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi's Recommended \NSouvenirs List!  \N{\c&H9E5ED4&}#1 will be revealed \Nafter the commercial  \N{\c&HC6A647&}#2 Oil blotting paper  \N#3 Raw yatsuhashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.34,list_00:32,Text,0000,0000,0000,,#1 will be revealed \Nafter the commercial
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:37.76,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,The number one souvenir would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.57,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Your wonderful memories, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:42.23,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sly, but cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:42.72,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.05,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiman, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:00.45,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:05.23,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say "Uno." Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:07.50,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:23.38,Ore_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.64,haunted_house_02:40,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Most Terrifying Haunted House in History
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.37,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:49.69,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God! Oh, God! Oh, God! \NOh, God! Oh, God! Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.76,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard a weird voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.90,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.06,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts in haunted houses aren't scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's really scary are people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There's that cynical attitude again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.99,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I find it kind of reliable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, haunted houses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.85,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,where people scare you \Nare the most terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.00,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! I can't rely on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:14.10,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Totsuka, you seem \Ntotally cool with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.38,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I like this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.13,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Kawasaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:27.85,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Kawasaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.90,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.26,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it hurt like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.08,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.67,haunted_house_02:40,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Most Terrifying Haunted House in History
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.52,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.26,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.70,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,That was really fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:07.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.31,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think we've played enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.06,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.42,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll get Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.44,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Wooden swords are so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.98,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ebina, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.15,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the haunted \Nhouse had any effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.01,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.34,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.42,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,This garden is also called "Tiger Cubs \NCrossing the Water," you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Which parts do you think are the tigers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Did that interest her \Nbecause tigers are cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.04,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She loves cats like they love Friskies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.20,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.41,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.69,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,How's that job coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.77,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty tough... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:14.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to push too hard and \Nmake Ebina-san like him less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.21,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's one person who can't catch a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.63,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Plus what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.65,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to leave this all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.70,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It's no substitute for actual help,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.01,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,but I have been thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.73,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Famous places in Kyoto \Nthat girls might like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.69,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.73,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're always on the ball, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.73,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.74,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.00,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.42,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Hikio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.42,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, what exactly are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.54,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop trying to mess with Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.41,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening. And we're \Nnot messing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.55,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are. It's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.33,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nuisance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.30,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who's asking \Nus to do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:30.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not like it \Nhurts you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:31.73,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.87,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:39.95,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If you're with Yui, \Nyou should know about Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm not "with" her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.62,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think I meant? Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.95,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,As if Yui would go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.64,love_sweaters_06:47,Text,0000,0000,0000,,We Love\NLong Knit\NSweaters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.64,coordinate_06:47,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinate casually \Nwith a girly knit sweater
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.64,gf_denim_06:47,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend denim
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.76,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.64,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I meant, if you talk with \NYui a lot, you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:53.91,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.64,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to add \Nthat on a second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.87,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ebina appeals to guys as \Nlong as she's not talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.36,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,so a lot of them ask to \Nbe introduced to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.65,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,But once they're introduced, \Nshe turns them down really gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.49,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was being shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.72,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I tried pretty hard to push things along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.06,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,But she laughed and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.95,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, never mind, then."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.55,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,As if I were a total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:24.27,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ebina doesn't talk about herself \Nmuch, and I don't ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.84,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think she \Nlikes that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you had to sacrifice many \Nthings to protect one,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:35.04,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,you're more likely to give \Nup and throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.64,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Including the relationships \Nyou have in your hand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.86,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a lot of fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.19,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd appreciate it if you didn't butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.55,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama said he'd do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.88,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:56.00,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if Hayato said that, then it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.21,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:06.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What a great view! I can see the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Break time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.20,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.21,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Tobecchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.88,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we meet again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.44,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hikitani-kun, you haven't forgotten \Nwhat we discussed, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.85,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How's it going among the men?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.15,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Happy and harmonious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting along fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.36,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They play cards together at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.19,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see that! \NThat's not tasty at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.41,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What I really want is for the guys to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.45,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,all close together where I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to Arashiyama, \Ntoo, so maybe then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.39,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.24,Randen_08:43,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1488,1)}Randen Arashiyama Station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to spoil your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:54.86,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.09,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can have it, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.54,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.81,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she just take one \Nlittle bite from each thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If we were splitting them \Nhalf-and-half, I'd eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.66,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do with these, Yukinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.13,Ore_Main,Yukinon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.69,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can eat some, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.37,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.81,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.73,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of feel like an animal being fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.36,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad. Food I didn't have \Nto work for tastes awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.48,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.13,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,This place is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.23,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... And look at the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Lanterns, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.81,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! I bet this is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:17.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.79,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,To be c-confessed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.13,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why the passive voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.18,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like a good location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.77,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.77,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If Tobe's going to go for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:39.10,Ore_Main,Toba,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! I'm getting nervous! Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.10,Ore_Main,Yamato,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.26,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe's getting a girlfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.75,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't want to \Nhang out with me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.65,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,That's so not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.58,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.58,Ore_Main,Yamato,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.83,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.72,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.09,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,What, Hayato-kun? I'm kinda \Nfreaking out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.05,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.33,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.40,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I was just going to say "good luck,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.93,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,but once I saw your face, \NI didn't feel like it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.93,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Harsh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.95,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little less nervous, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're being awfully uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.11,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:22.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it felt as if you \Nwere trying to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.21,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.36,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I just like things as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:33.07,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I like Tobe and Hina, and the \Ntime we all spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.10,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If this is enough to ruin that, \Nwas it really that strong to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.06,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.89,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What's lost won't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's more ridiculous that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.02,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to enjoy superficial \Nrelationships like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.28,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.17,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think of it as superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:56.33,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the environment \NI'm in is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tobe, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.70,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I told him over and over to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.90,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Hina opening her \Nheart to him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.45,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I don't know \Nwhat's in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.31,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't want Tobe to \Nrush to a conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty selfish thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's just for your own convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.10,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.34,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.09,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What I'd do doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.68,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking "If it were \Nme..." is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.86,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama isn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.18,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Neither is Tobe, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.90,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How I think or feel means \Nnothing whatsoever,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.19,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and it's pointless to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, you don't \Nwant anything to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.32,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.41,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last person I wanted to turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.43,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling is mutual, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what \NHayama's trying to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.27,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.20,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Hikitani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.99,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,This is nuts! I'm totally \Nfreaking out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, what'll you do if she rejects you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.99,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kinda harsh to say \Nthat before I tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.38,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebina-san will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.00,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I still wouldn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.09,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a very serious person, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.63,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:45.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then do the best you \Ncan, until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.19,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.97,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good guy after all, Hikitani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I am not, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So you can be nice, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.05,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.29,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,At the rate it's going, \NTobe will be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.02,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.11,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For what it's worth, there's a \Nway to wrap this all up neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.17,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.12,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.82,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.24,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.99,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, there's no \Ndoubt she'll turn him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe must be somewhat prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.45,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.61,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe isn't the only one who \Nvalues their relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:03.00,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she came to us with that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.30,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why he suffered so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.64,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.41,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to keep it in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.14,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing all three of them want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.51,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.51,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.83,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,To not see Tobe get rejected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:22.70,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and to keep their group close while \Nstaying good friends with Ebina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:26.61,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's really only one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.55,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.57,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.32,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:42.93,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.56,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.01,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to go out \Nwith anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:15.19,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who tells me they like \Nme, I won't go out with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.27,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you wanted, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:32.73,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Hikitani-kun, that wasn't cool, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.55,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm glad I found out \Nbefore she could reject me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.06,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,but that was not cool. So not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.08,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That just means this isn't the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.00,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with enjoying \Nthe friendship you have now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.57,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.65,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,She did say "right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.27,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Hikitani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.36,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I won't let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.46,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.17,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.99,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that was the only way \Nyou knew how to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.74,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.48,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the way you do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.08,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It frustrates me that I \Ncan't explain why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate that you \Nhandle things that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.88,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.16,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Should we head back, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.72,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that plan failed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.02,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I was definitely surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.68,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Hina didn't get to say what \Nshe wanted to either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But... I was pretty shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.82,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I thought you were serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.57,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.49,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.34,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stuff like that again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:42.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It was the most effective way. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:45.12,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about effectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.10,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There are some people who \Ndon't want a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Some want things to stay the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to make things \Nconvenient for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:54.17,Ore_Italics,HachiIn,0000,0000,0000,,And as I'm saying all this, it hits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.25,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So the only option is to find a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.68,Ore_Italics,HachiIn,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just rationalizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.61,Ore_Italics,HachiIn,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of deception I hated \Nmore than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.16,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Tobecchi didn't get rejected,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:04.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and the guys seem to be getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.04,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hina didn't have to worry, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.92,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Now things will be back to \Nnormal from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.79,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe nothing will have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.39,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But... But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.43,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You should give more thought \Nto how other people feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:27.13,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,How is it you understand so much, \Nbut you don't understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.31,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.09,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.36,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.09,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.79,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't resolve the thing \Nyou consulted me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:10.35,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Not on the surface, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.45,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You understood, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted me to get the guys closer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,so you could keep them at \Na distance from yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:21.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and stop Tobe from confessing \Nto you before it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You probably talked to \NHayama about this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Hayama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:28.12,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,became stressed and had no choice \Nbut to act the way he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.29,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything you did. \NIt really helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:36.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe's an idiot and a loser, \Nbut he's a nice guy, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.74,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:41.63,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I hooked up with someone \Nright now, it wouldn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:42.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:43.95,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.14,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.12,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no helping that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.10,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, there's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:01.65,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'd be able to go out \Nwith you, Hikitani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.82,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you say stuff carelessly, \Nsomeone might fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.44,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of like the way you \Ncan be so honest with people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.71,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,who don't matter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.19,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.91,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of like that about myself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.67,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can appreciate a \Nperson who can say things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.20,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't mean so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:35.18,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I like myself and \Neverything around me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:38.71,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt like that in ages, \Nso I don't want to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:43.11,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I like where I am, and I like \Nthe people here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.33,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.29,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.37,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's precious, \Nbecause you don't want to lose it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.21,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,you hide it away and put up a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.96,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:01.80,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.73,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest liar of all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.04,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,His and Her Love Confessions \NWill Reach No One.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:07.06,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:24:08.42,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#03 Quietly, Yukinoshita Yukino Makes a Decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:43.14,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sure is quiet without Onii-chan around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.68,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right, Ka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:50.10,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I hope Onii-chan's getting along okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.33,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right, Ka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:55.53,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's so boring without Onii-chan around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.08,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ka-kun, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.72,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good kitty, good kitty! You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.30,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Your fur's so smooth! \NGood kitty, good kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.76,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Ka-kun! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:08.42,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I hope he comes home soon.
